---
title: BeaconLink Agent Registration Workflow
---

flowchart TB

    %% =====================================================
    %% Agent Bootstrap
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Bootstrap["Agent Bootstrap"]

        Install["Install BeaconLink Agent"]
        Config["Bootstrap Configuration"]
        Identity["Agent Identity"]
        Start["Agent Startup"]

    end

    Install --> Config
    Config --> Identity
    Identity --> Start

    %% =====================================================
    %% Initial Connection
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Connection["Secure Relay Connection"]

        Discover["Discover Relay"]
        TLS["Mutual TLS Handshake"]
        Authenticate["Authenticate"]
        Session["Establish Secure Session"]

    end

    Start --> Discover
    Discover --> TLS
    TLS --> Authenticate
    Authenticate --> Session

    %% =====================================================
    %% Registration Service
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Control["Control Plane Registration"]

        Gateway["API Gateway"]
        Registry["Agent Registry"]
        IdentityService["Identity Service"]
        Certificate["Certificate Authority"]

    end

    Session --> Gateway
    Gateway --> IdentityService
    IdentityService --> Registry
    IdentityService --> Certificate

    %% =====================================================
    %% Registration Exchange
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Registration["Registration Process"]

        Metadata["Agent Metadata

• Agent ID
• Version
• Platform
• Architecture
• Runtime Capabilities
• Labels
• Site Information"]

        Validate["Validate Registration"]
        Approve["Registration Approved"]
        Credentials["Issue Credentials"]

    end

    Registry --> Metadata
    Metadata --> Validate
    Validate --> Approve
    Approve --> Credentials

    %% =====================================================
    %% Capability Discovery
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Discovery["Capability Discovery"]

        Runtime["Runtime Detection"]
        Plugins["Plugin Discovery"]
        Resources["Resource Discovery"]
        Inventory["Inventory Update"]

    end

    Credentials --> Runtime
    Runtime --> Plugins
    Plugins --> Resources
    Resources --> Inventory

    %% =====================================================
    %% Operational State
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Operations["Operational State"]

        Online["Agent Online"]
        Heartbeat["Heartbeat"]
        Status["Status Updates"]
        Metrics["Metrics"]
        Events["Platform Events"]

    end

    Inventory --> Online

    Online --> Heartbeat
    Online --> Status
    Online --> Metrics

    Heartbeat --> Events
    Status --> Events
    Metrics --> Events

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    Heartbeat -. Periodic .-> Registry
    Status -. Continuous .-> Registry
    Metrics -. Streaming .-> Registry

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Failure["Failure Scenarios"]

        Retry["Retry Registration"]
        Expired["Credential Rotation"]
        Offline["Agent Offline"]
        Reconnect["Reconnect"]

    end

    Authenticate -->|Failure| Retry
    Retry --> Discover

    Certificate --> Expired
    Expired --> TLS

    Heartbeat --> Offline
    Offline --> Reconnect
    Reconnect --> Discover

    %% =====================================================
    %% Security Principles
    %% =====================================================

    Security["Security Principles

• Mutual TLS
• Zero Trust
• Outbound Connections Only
• Short-Lived Credentials
• Certificate Rotation
• Identity Verification
• Capability Validation
• Fully Auditable Registration"]

    Security -.-> Connection
    Security -.-> Registration

    %% =====================================================
    %% Registration Outcomes
    %% =====================================================

    Outcomes["Registration Results

• Trusted Identity
• Runtime Inventory
• Capability Catalog
• Site Association
• Secure Communication
• Deployment Eligibility"]

    Outcomes -.-> Operations

